x_fmt=jpeg\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6657407407407407\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZRz6nVVHJJoT6R0qBptm6fE5SmhYj1xZibJELDQRP2NOAGEGIjGZuvUWibeWbFwA8ia081kDHQWUKDIA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-index=\"50\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZRz6nVVHJJoT6R0qBptm6fE5SmhYj1xZibJELDQRP2NOAGEGIjGZuvUWibeWbFwA8ia081kDHQWUKDIA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: unset;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">据深圳市气象台消息——</p><p><br></p><p>深圳市气象台12月21日16时00分将全市寒冷黄色预警信号升级为橙色，信号可能持续2-3天。</p><p><br></p></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24563318777292575\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dY1NaysichZRz6nVVHJJoT6R0qBptm6fEiaMTu8FjvvqicjzmshH9pLRLA5naSaIApsupRLygGeKsLHT4ORnaxeiaA/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-w=\"916\" data-index=\"51\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dY1NaysichZRz6nVVHJJoT6R0qBptm6fEiaMTu8FjvvqicjzmshH9pLRLA5naSaIApsupRLygGeKsLHT4ORnaxeiaA/640?wx_fmt=png\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: unset;\"><p><br></p><p><strong>22日</strong>我市中北部最低气温降至4℃左右，南部最低气温5-6℃，白天最高气温11℃，沿海高地最大阵风7-8级，体感寒冷。<br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>23-25日</strong>最低气温维持在5-7℃，天气持续寒冷，白天可见阳光，空气干燥。</p><p><br></p><p><strong>26日</strong>起寒冷天气逐渐缓和，气温逐日回升，但早晚仍较冷。</p><p><br></p></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2285191956124315\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dvqxUbIjRCWXP53TfQXQeoXv7hR0aQE0iax5yC5OmGNd1gV4pzyk7icUicSsAh13Pv6ic35ggY6arLMW9OS45decSA/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-w=\"547\" data-index=\"52\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dvqxUbIjRCWXP53TfQXQeoXv7hR0aQE0iax5yC5OmGNd1gV4pzyk7icUicSsAh13Pv6ic35ggY6arLMW9OS45decSA/640?wx_fmt=png\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><p>寒冷橙色预警发布之后</p><p>我们要注意什么呢？</p></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.9695652173913043\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZRz6nVVHJJoT6R0qBptm6fE0RmgrLO9YTa91IR8IC8rmogToSZYyk1ZStl5nz09cbDguiaFl5Pa9KA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-w=\"690\" data-index=\"53\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZRz6nVVHJJoT6R0qBptm6fE0RmgrLO9YTa91IR8IC8rmogToSZYyk1ZStl5nz09cbDguiaFl5Pa9KA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: unset;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><strong>温 馨 提 示</strong></span><br></p><p><br></p><p>寒冷天气持续时间较长，请注意防寒保暖，尤其是小孩、体弱者和老人要做好防寒措施、预防心脑血管等疾病。</p><p><br></p><p>使用燃气热水器时注意保持室内通风，防止一氧化碳中毒。</p><p><br></p><p>冷空气影响期间阵风较大，请注意做好防风措施。</p><p><br></p></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.07875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dvqxUbIjRCVfMwoWqGWKVVXtLkvSa2KA34ib1RKxY2w00ryDNI5FXEMYQ0wibRYrQEUvBS1OABRF4stFSeoeibB2A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-w=\"800\" data-index=\"54\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dvqxUbIjRCVfMwoWqGWKVVXtLkvSa2KA34ib1RKxY2w00ryDNI5FXEMYQ0wibRYrQEUvBS1OABRF4stFSeoeibB2A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><p><br></p><p>官微君在此提醒：</p><p>冷空气来袭</p><p>正在备战考研</p><p>期末复习的你们</p><p>一定要注意添衣保暖</p><p>小心感冒哦！</p></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>部分内容源自深圳天气</p><p>图片｜深技大人的朋友圈&nbsp;</p><p>安全保卫中心 食堂</p><p>编辑｜雯玉</p><p>审核｜钟鑫</p></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.3888888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dY1NaysichZRMBJovN1SnIVHSnXn4dqgeVvURYq4vt56Wu7FLF9jASy8WIsXLkHJNsibia9SOdibN7rKyic2SS0vjQQ/640?wx_fmt=gif\" data-w=\"648\" data-index=\"55\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dY1NaysichZRMBJovN1SnIVHSnXn4dqgeVvURYq4vt56Wu7FLF9jASy8WIsXLkHJNsibia9SOdibN7rKyic2SS0vjQQ/640?wx_fmt=gif\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\" data-order=\"1\"></section></section></section></div>', 1, '4598f07598f9676cdd7b15cf1ceb1772', '2023-12-23 14:33:12', 20231223);
