ong></p></section></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><p><span>大学生程序设计竞赛有一个传统，队伍每通过一道题目，就会获得一个与题目对应颜色的气球，在赛场上气球的数量是队伍实力的象征。本次比赛，深技大为选手们准备了印有“I<span>♥</span>SZTU”与“I<span>♥</span>CCPC”的心形气球和精美的气球挂件，每个气球用绳子带着小挂件摆在桌面上，改变了过往在选手身旁绑气球的方式，款式多样的挂件也让赛场更为有趣。</span></p><p><br></p></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><section><img data-ratio=\"0.512962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicEU60NrXEKbh3TK950jX6WgFYqN3bLHAgOC5I6jTln8KPKCUmsulDiaA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-index=\"15\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicEU60NrXEKbh3TK950jX6WgFYqN3bLHAgOC5I6jTln8KPKCUmsulDiaA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p><span>每道题第一个答出的队伍，会获得这道题的“特别气球”以作区分，深技大特别设计了印有赛事logo与学校校徽的18寸超大气球，在场馆中格外令人瞩目。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><section><img data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicQJkyPv5XhAf8amVnaWv0X2uVWO8OHhkTqJlpqliaRgFFZLQ9klyEjrA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-index=\"16\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicQJkyPv5XhAf8amVnaWv0X2uVWO8OHhkTqJlpqliaRgFFZLQ9klyEjrA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><section><img data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" 