section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><p><span><em><strong>SZTU</strong></em></span></p></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p><em><strong>03</strong></em></p></section></section><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p><strong>深技大教师开发，</strong></p><p><strong>CCPC官方认可的比赛系统</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><p><span>程序设计竞赛需要一个软件平台，需支持选手们提交解题代码，录入队伍信息与题目信息，完成比赛评测、榜单计算、机位抽签等众多功能。在过往的赛事中，比赛系统多种多样，诸多功能也需要不同的软件支持。深技大大数据与互联网学院ACM集训队教练郭云镝老师为赛事开发了一个集成全套比赛流程功能的“一站式比赛系统”，经与CCPC组委会调试，今年首次在国赛亮相，为比赛的顺利进行提供了有力技术保障，受到了选手的喜爱和组委会的认可。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span>系统独创了移动端气球任务队列，志愿者可以用手机获取所负责区域的气球任务，并进行标记。PC端全局管理界面可以了解气球任务分配、分布实时状态，极大提升了管理效率，让赛场气球发放工作更为稳定有序。</span></p><p><br></p></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><section><img data-ratio=\"0.5175925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicECvBrExpu3kV5ysudlc3zNwribiaoaDux7w6rLibcDPSMu4yiagl5o28HQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-index=\"18\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicECvBrExpu3kV5ysudlc3zNwribiaoaDux7w6rLibcDPSMu4yiagl5o28HQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section style=\"text-align: center;\"><p><span><em>▲</em></span><span><em></em></span><em><span>气球队列与气球管理</span></em></p></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p><span>该系统还集成了“滚榜”所需的复杂算法，使赛事流程衔接流畅。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><section><img data-ratio=\"0.5166666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"720\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicKQsWwicZ1drTLSMLqicQSOecEaibjH7fUYicficYOjpgtvXdXUqMMOMY22g/640?wx_fmt=gif\" data-index=\"19\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicKQsWwicZ1drTLSMLqicQSOecEaibjH7fUYicficYOjpgtvXdXUqMMOMY22g/640?wx_fmt=gif\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\" class=\"__bg_gif\" data-order=\"2\"></section></section></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section style=\"text-align: center;\"><p><span><em>▲</em></span><span><em></em></span><em><span>集成的滚榜系统</span></em></p></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><img data-ratio=\"0.5527777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicXLsqwVJNInojPMzlFWhmYaxWG6f5aOVicuJVxQwdI6s1IO6HeXDyrEg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-index=\"20\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicXLsqwVJNInojPMzlFWhmYaxWG6f5aOVicuJVxQwdI6s1IO6HeXDyrEg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\"></svg></section></section></section></section><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\"></svg></section></section></section></section><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\"></svg></section></section></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><p><span>本次比赛进行了5小时全程线上直播，由GDCPC 2023外省冠军、武汉大学王骏峣，比赛裁判组组长、清华大学迟凯文，深技大学生志愿者叶曼君进行直播解说。大数据与互联网学院ACM算法与程序设计创新实验室师生合作，为比赛系统添加了直播控件，可实时获取场内比赛数据合成在直播画面中，使收看比赛的观众们实时了解场内题目通过情况、数据分布和排名变化。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><img data-ratio=\"0.45\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOica0TevuAFtbTJicgalpBDHVulUdb5ZlMTfEvlbQsjcLYsk3uQcC7713g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-index=\"21\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOica0TevuAFtbTJicgalpBDHVulUdb5ZlMTfEvlbQsjcLYsk3uQcC7713g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><img data-ratio=\"0.5578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"640\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOic2VjAW6LotlVib7j2KogQDDaljNlmRic9M2r3nrnOUSJDhpOSCDEFVlPQ/640?wx_fmt=gif\" data-index=\"22\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOic2VjAW6LotlVib7j2KogQDDaljNlmRic9M2r3nrnOUSJDhpOSCDEFVlPQ/640?wx_fmt=gif\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\" class=\"__bg_gif\" data-order=\"3\"></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><img data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicxX2ibt5CXanBZbY78icGBDPrdyh78FP8GzoRJ86V74w4BXT9obNnQYZQ/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-index=\"23\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicxX2ibt5CXanBZbY78icGBDPrdyh78FP8GzoRJ86V74w4BXT9obNnQYZQ/640?wx_fmt=png\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><p><span><em><strong>SZTU</strong></em></span></p></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p><em><strong>04</strong></em></p></section></section><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p><strong>超五千平的比赛场地</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><p><span>2600平米的羽毛球馆赛场和3100平米的综合馆观摩区同步开放。为进一步增强观摩人员的观摩真实性，学校在场地内距离赛区约4米位置设置了“比赛观摩通道”，在不影响选手比赛的同时让更多人了解CCPC赛事的魅力所在。</span></p><p><br></p></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><section><img data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicYPsbtFTcia5a3kYibscOBmY4Km9fsHWibT6553lSpiauZhlZyPGKl0m01Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-index=\"24\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicYPsbtFTcia5a3kYibscOBmY4Km9fsHWibT6553lSpiauZhlZyPGKl0m01Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><section><img data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicIlnQ6cMYwUEyYKHaOVvyP8uEADeR0hgQlIDZ73SSEUG8Ba5iblQ9QgQ/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-index=\"25\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicIlnQ6cMYwUEyYKHaOVvyP8uEADeR0hgQlIDZ73SSEUG8Ba5iblQ9QgQ/640?wx_fmt=png\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p><span>精心设计的校徽墙，美观大气的横幅、合影墙，进入赛场的“龙门”……深技大校园充满了比赛气氛。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOiceffFAyb1pF3uCdMAJE0bH3rCCSW1H9Fmw2huuE4icFicBiaSYYEyTne8w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-index=\"26\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOiceffFAyb1pF3uCdMAJE0bH3rCCSW1H9Fmw2huuE4icFicBiaSYYEyTne8w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><p><span><em><strong>SZTU</strong></em></span></p></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p><em><strong>05</strong></em></p></section></section><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p><strong>如“开盲盒”一般有趣的纪念品</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><p><span>赛前，深技大向参赛选手发起了诙谐有趣的“假代码”征集活动，还通过程序生成了极难的“数独游戏”，并以这两项活动为灵感设计了赛事纪念品，让不少选手沉浸在“开盲盒”的喜悦中。</span></p><p><br></p></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><section><img data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicrtUmgC4IRCToW2nuJBFsMNClvrOzghfsBQ9kIoPenHiaheibUNoYas4g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-index=\"27\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicrtUmgC4IRCToW2nuJBFsMNClvrOzghfsBQ9kIoPenHiaheibUNoYas4g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><p><span><em><strong>SZTU</strong></em></span></p></section></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p><em><strong>06</strong></em></p></section></section><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p><strong>赛事专属的无人机表演</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><p><span>大数据与互联网学院无人机协会在比赛前夜为来自全国的朋友们准备了一场专属的无人机表演秀，组成了包括CCPC logo、SZTU-ACM等多种图形，展现了深技大人的热情。</span></p><p><br></p></section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><section><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><section><img data-ratio=\"0.375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicmiaQJGnibPa5cWBOP2O3gm596GicHWvBTGoCTrnIM4UaSsgQEIR2z5stg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-index=\"28\" _width=\"100%\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dY1NaysichZTHRIwccictrFsmuiaPuoYicOicmiaQJGnibPa5cWBOP2O3gm596GicHWvBTGoCTrnIM4UaSsgQEIR2z5stg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" __sec_open_place_holder__=\"true\"></section></section></section></section><p powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><br></p><section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section><p><span><em><strong>SZTU</strong></em></span></p></section>